#. type: findex
#: misc.texi.orig:1782
#, no-wrap
msgid "ps-print-region"
msgstr "ps-print-region"

#. type: findex
#: misc.texi.orig:1783
#, no-wrap
msgid "ps-print-buffer"
msgstr "ps-print-buffer"

#. type: findex
#: misc.texi.orig:1784
#, no-wrap
msgid "ps-print-region-with-faces"
msgstr "ps-print-region-with-faces"

#. type: findex
#: misc.texi.orig:1785
#, no-wrap
msgid "ps-print-buffer-with-faces"
msgstr "ps-print-buffer-with-faces"

#. type: Plain text
#: misc.texi.orig:1792
msgid ""
"The @code{ps-print-buffer} and @code{ps-print-region} commands print buffer "
"contents in PostScript form.  One command prints the entire buffer; the "
"other, just the region.  The commands @code{ps-print-buffer-with-faces} and "
"@code{ps-print-region-with-faces} behave similarly, but use PostScript "
"features to show the faces (fonts and colors) of the buffer text."
msgstr "@code{ps-print-buffer}および@code{ps-print-region}コマンドは、バッファーの内容をPostScript形式で印刷します。一方はバッファー全体を印刷し、もう一方はリージョンだけを印刷します。コマンド@code{ps-print-buffer-with-faces}および@code{ps-print-region-with-faces}も同様に振る舞いますが、バッファーテキストのフェイス(フォントとカラー)を表示するためにPostScript機能を使用します。"

#. type: Plain text
#: misc.texi.orig:1796
msgid ""
"Interactively, when you use a prefix argument (@kbd{C-u}), the command "
"prompts the user for a file name, and saves the PostScript image in that "
"file instead of sending it to the printer."
msgstr "プレフィクス引数(@kbd{C-u})を使用した場合、このコマンドは対話的にユーザーにファイル名の入力を求め、PostScriptイメージをプリンターに送るかわりに、そのファイルに保存します。"

#. type: findex
#: misc.texi.orig:1797
#, no-wrap
msgid "ps-spool-region"
msgstr "ps-spool-region"

